data.description:
Great First-Time Homebuyer Opportunity. Come look at this neat & tidy 3 BR ranch home situated on a cul-de-sac in town.
Home offers 1080 sq ft of living space living. Nice living room with a trey ceiling & laminate wood flooring.  Kitchen has nice cabinetry and comes equipped with a refrigerator and range/oven.  Separate dining room and three bedrooms. Nice rear deck for all your outdoor enjoyment.  Out building offers extra storage
